<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>At FarmTrack, we are committed to protecting your privacy. This page outlines how we handle and protect the data you share with us.</p>

<h3>Data Collection and Storage</h3>
<p>FarmTrack stores user-provided information, such as reminders and email addresses, in a secure database. This information enables us to deliver essential functionalities like reminder notifications and scheduling. Access to stored data is restricted and managed in accordance with industry best practices.</p>

<h3>Email Notifications</h3>
<p>FarmTrack uses an email notification service powered by Gmail to send reminders and notifications to registered email addresses. We use a dedicated Gmail account, and emails are sent only when reminders are due. Email addresses are stored securely and used solely for sending these notifications.</p>

<h3>Data Privacy</h3>
<p>Your data will not be shared with third parties or used for any purposes other than those directly related to FarmTrack’s functionalities. All information you provide is securely stored, and we strive to follow best practices to protect your data.</p>

<p>If you have any questions regarding our privacy practices, feel free to contact us.</p>
